That's the only explanation.

45
00:05:08,583 --> 00:05:11,500
Call it "Destiny in Asagaya."
'S got a ring, right?

46
00:05:11,583 --> 00:05:13,166
[GIRL 1A laughs]
Yeah, no.

47
00:05:13,250 --> 00:05:15,083
[GIRL 1B] Seriously.
This place is a joke.

48
00:05:15,166 --> 00:05:16,958
[TSUTOMU] Aw, c'mon
don't be that way.

49
00:05:17,041 --> 00:05:19,291
[TSUTOMU] Shibuya and
Shinjuku are so predictable.

50
00:05:19,375 --> 00:05:21,416
Think about it:
They're tourist traps.

51
00:05:21,500 --> 00:05:24,625
Meeting the love of your life in
Asagaya? You don't expect that.

52
00:05:24,708 --> 00:05:26,625
It's a surprise. It's special.

53
00:05:26,708 --> 00:05:29,333
Right? Ya don't see sump'm
comin', it stays with ya.

54
