Oh.

77
00:07:09,583 --> 00:07:12,375
[KOKONE]
Th-Th-Thank you.

78
00:07:12,458 --> 00:07:14,208
I was nearby and
heard your voice.

79
00:07:14,291 --> 00:07:15,750
When there's a cry for help,

80
00:07:15,833 --> 00:07:19,875
I come running ready to lend
a hand wherever there's a need.

81
00:07:19,958 --> 00:07:21,333
I have to...

82
