...because I am The Savior.

83
00:07:42,916 --> 00:07:44,500
It was certainly
nice of him to help,

84
00:07:44,583 --> 00:07:46,875
but maybe the poor young man's
spent a little too much time

85
00:07:46,958 --> 00:07:48,208
in the sun.

86
00:07:48,291 --> 00:07:49,333
Huh?

87
00:07:55,458 --> 00:07:57,000
Hmm.

88
00:08:04,458 --> 00:08:06,833
Now is the time for rejoicing.

89
00:08:06,916 --> 00:08:10,416
For today I deign
to set you free!

90
00:08:14,166 --> 00:08:21,166
[eerie wailing]

91
00:08:21,250 --> 00:08:26,458
[M.J.B.K. TWIST]
Maaaaaakiiii!

92
00:08:32,291 --> 00:08:33,458
--Huh?
--[GIRL STUDENT 1C] What is it?

93
00:08:33,541 --> 00:08:34,625
[GIRL STUDENT 1B]
Something wrong?

94
00:08:34,708 --> 00:08:37,208
[SOUGON] Injected
with the Nesta Virus,

95
00:08:37,291 --> 00:08:42,958
