writhe to life, become bestial.

96
00:08:43,041 --> 00:08:45,833
What happens next
is enthralling.

97
00:08:50,166 --> 00:08:52,041
[MALE SUSHI CHEF 1A]
Huh? What the?

98
00:08:55,250 --> 00:08:56,583
[HAYATO]
I'm very sorry, but..

99
00:08:56,666 --> 00:08:58,250
...if you'll please excuse me.

100
00:08:58,333 --> 00:09:00,750
[HATANO] Hey!
Kujyo, where're you going?

101
00:09:00,833 --> 00:09:03,416
[SOUGON] That which in the
mundane world corresponds

102
00:09:03,500 --> 00:09:05,125
to the character
reacts violently.

103
00:09:05,208 --> 00:09:07,291
Somebody help me!

104
00:09:07,375 --> 00:09:08,625
[SOUGON]
The concept runs amok,

105
00:09:08,708 --> 00:09:12,208
like a wild animal
freed from its tether.

106
00:09:12,291 --> 00:09:14,333
Unbelievable, right?

107
00:09:14,416 --> 00:09:16,625
[GIRL 1B laughs]
It doesn't have any twists!

108
00:09:16,708 --> 00:09:18,791
That's hilarious!

109
00:09:18,875 --> 00:09:20,541
What's up with
all that noise?

110
00:09:20,625 --> 00:09:23,166
--[HAYATO] Hey! Look out!
--[TSUTOMU] Heads up!

111
00:09:27,083 --> 00:09:29,416
