flattened us. Idiot!

112
00:09:29,500 --> 00:09:31,208
[HAYATO]
Are you guys okay?

113
00:09:31,291 --> 00:09:32,916
[TSUTOMU]
Hayato?

114
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:34,708
Tsutomu? What're you...?

115
00:09:36,333 --> 00:09:38,416
[BOY 1A] Doesn't
that belong to Kokone?

116
00:09:38,500 --> 00:09:39,666
To whom?

117
00:09:39,750 --> 00:09:43,750
[BOY 1A] Seriously?
Kokone of Shiroboco!

118
00:09:43,833 --> 00:09:45,708
[AKIRA]
So that was real.

119
00:09:45,791 --> 00:09:48,583
This is handmade.
She'll want it back.

120
00:09:48,666 --> 00:09:52,916
[distant sirens]

121
