[OLD LADY 1A sighs] I spoil
my grandchildren terribly.

122
00:09:56,125 --> 00:09:57,583
Thank you so much, sweetheart,

123
00:09:57,666 --> 00:09:58,875
I don't know what
possessed me to think

124
00:09:58,958 --> 00:10:00,958
I could carry all
these toys by myself.

125
00:10:01,041 --> 00:10:02,416
Good thing you insisted.

126
00:10:02,500 --> 00:10:04,541
Oh, uh, I...

127
00:10:04,625 --> 00:10:05,625
--Huh?
--Huh?

128
00:10:10,500 --> 00:10:14,791
[sirens]

129
00:10:14,875 --> 00:10:15,666
[people screaming]

130
00:10:15,750 --> 00:10:16,333
[OLD LADY 1A]
Augh!

131
00:10:16,416 --> 00:10:17,875
[KOKONE]
Get down!

132
00:10:19,625 --> 00:10:22,708
A twister? Then this must be...

133
00:10:22,791 --> 00:10:24,333
[MAN grunting]

134
00:10:24,416 --> 00:10:27,458
[SHOKO] Hold still, will ya?
I'll try'n cut it loose.

135
00:10:29,166 --> 00:10:31,375
