[MAIA] We've had this
discussion, Subete.

138
00:10:38,583 --> 00:10:40,666
No eating in the cockpit.

139
00:10:40,750 --> 00:10:43,083
[SUBETE]
Right. Sorry, Maia.

140
00:10:44,333 --> 00:10:46,291
At long last
the time has come.

141
00:10:46,375 --> 00:10:49,625
I shall fulfill the mission
and meet my destiny.

142
00:11:01,208 --> 00:11:04,416
[WOMAN 1A grunts]
Get this off of me.

143
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:09,625
[AKIRA]
Hey!

144
00:11:09,708 --> 00:11:10,833
It's y-you.

145
00:11:10,916 --> 00:11:12,250
[AKIRA]
Perfect timing.

146
00:11:12,333 --> 00:11:14,833
[KOKONE] I'm s-sorry,
I uh, I can't talk right now.

147
00:11:14,916 --> 00:11:16,125
I have to go!

148
00:11:16,208 --> 00:11:17,166
Hang on a sec.

149
00:11:17,250 --> 00:11:18,791
No! Let go of me!

150
00:11:18,875 --> 00:11:20,041
There's no time!

151
00:11:20,125 --> 00:11:24,000
The world is...
I mean, it's in... I have to go!

152
00:11:28,125 --> 00:11:29,875
[KOKONE gasps]
S-Sorry I'm late!

153
00:11:29,958 --> 00:11:32,708
[TSUTOMU] Nice of you
to join us, Kokone.

154
00:11:35,333 --> 00:11:36,416
[SAKURAKO]
Attention please.

155
00:11:36,500 --> 00:11:38,458
The café is closed
until further notice.

156
00:11:38,541 --> 00:11:40,291
Sorry for the inconvenience.

157
00:11:40,375 --> 00:11:41,166
[KENTO]
Thanks for droppin' by.

158
00:11:41,250 --> 00:11:43,291
We'll see you again real soon.

159
00:11:47,291 --> 00:11:48,458
[KENTO]
Help you?

160
00:11:50,541 --> 00:11:51,708
[HAYATO]
Manager?

161
00:11:51,791 --> 00:11:53,750
[SAKURAKO] You may
dispense with that title.

162
00:11:59,166 --> 00:12:00,208
[SAKURAKO]
From this point forward,

163
00:12:00,291 --> 00:12:02,250
