as "Commander."

164
00:12:02,333 --> 00:12:04,166
DEAVA System, activate!

165
00:12:26,583 --> 00:12:28,000
--[MALE B] Right.
--[FEMALE A] We're online.

166
00:12:28,083 --> 00:12:29,583
--[MALE B] All systems go.
--[FEMALE A] Vector machines.

167
00:12:29,666 --> 00:12:30,541
--[FEMALE A] Standby for launch.
--[MALE A] Launch platforms...

168
00:12:30,625 --> 00:12:32,041
...at the ready.

169
00:12:32,125 --> 00:12:34,208
[SAKURAKO] Formation: Delta.
Kujyo and Domon, you're up.

170
00:12:34,291 --> 00:12:35,416
Get in there.

171
00:12:35,500 --> 00:12:36,083
[HAYATO]
Roger.

172
00:12:36,166 --> 00:12:36,833
[TSUTOMU]
On it.

173
00:12:39,750 --> 00:12:41,291
So you're sending
us out for real?

174
00:12:41,375 --> 00:12:42,833
Not to be "that guy,"

175
00:12:42,916 --> 00:12:45,041
but you know I've never actually
been in one of these before.

176
00:12:45,125 --> 00:12:46,208
[SAKURAKO]
You'll be fine.

177
00:12:46,291 --> 00:12:47,666
This is what you've
been training for.

178
00:12:47,750 --> 00:12:50,250
