194
00:14:16,291 --> 00:14:18,708
I hope Tsutomu
and Hayato are ready.

195
00:14:18,791 --> 00:14:20,500
Do not falter.

196
00:14:20,583 --> 00:14:24,041
[AKIRA] Oh. So that's what
everyone's panicking about?

197
00:14:24,125 --> 00:14:24,916
[SHOKO]
Who the...?

198
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:25,916
[KOKONE]
You fuh followed me?

199
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:26,458
[SAKURAKO]
How did you get in here?

200
00:14:26,541 --> 00:14:28,083
Where's Kento?

201
00:14:33,708 --> 00:14:36,666
[KOKONE] No! W-W-Wait.
He's not dangerous!

202
00:14:36,750 --> 00:14:38,666
[SAKURAKO] Kikogami.
Do you know this guy?

203
00:14:38,750 --> 00:14:40,375
[KOKONE]
Well, I... I...

204
00:14:40,458 --> 00:14:42,333
[AKIRA]
Put me up there.

205
00:14:42,416 --> 00:14:44,375
[AKIRA] That thing's a
threat to the world, right?

206
00:14:44,458 --> 00:14:46,333
Let me destroy it for you.

207
00:14:46,416 --> 00:14:48,625
Put me in one of those machines.

208
00:14:48,708 --> 00:14:50,208
I do not take orders from...

209
