[AKIRA] With this hand,
I will save the world.

210
00:14:55,041 --> 00:14:56,791
For I am The Savior.

211
00:14:56,875 --> 00:14:59,416
What a cheese ball.

212
00:14:59,500 --> 00:15:01,041
[SAKURAKO]
This isn't a game, son,

213
00:15:01,125 --> 00:15:02,875
