time to indulge you.

214
00:15:02,958 --> 00:15:04,416
Get him out of here!

215
00:15:04,500 --> 00:15:05,416
--[MALE SECURITY 1A] Ma'am.
--[MALE SECURITY 1B] Roger that.

216
00:15:05,500 --> 00:15:06,458
[MALE SECURITY 1A]
Move it, kid.

217
00:15:06,541 --> 00:15:07,125
[MALE SECURITY 1B] 
No funny stuff.

