219
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:19,916
[M.J.B.K. TWIST]
Maki!

220
00:15:22,625 --> 00:15:23,750
You have Verbalism!

221
00:15:23,833 --> 00:15:25,041
That's supposed
to be the only power

