227
00:15:35,291 --> 00:15:42,291
[HAYATO]
Let's do this!

228
00:15:42,375 --> 00:15:43,375
What's happening?

229
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:48,791
What's the big fuss?

230
00:15:48,875 --> 00:15:50,166
All we have to do is guard him.

231
00:15:50,250 --> 00:15:52,083
Conditions for victory
couldn't be better!

232
00:15:52,166 --> 00:15:53,916
Don't start getting
careless on me.

233
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:55,416
Yeah, yeah.
Whatever. I know.

234
00:15:55,500 --> 00:15:58,166
Our duty is to Master
Sougon's sublime ideal.

235
00:15:58,250 --> 00:16:00,083
eliminating all who interfere.

236
00:16:00,166 --> 00:16:02,250
[SUBETE]
Absolutely. Well said, Maia.

237
00:16:03,500 --> 00:16:05,958
Is this what the Commander
was talking about?

238
00:16:06,041 --> 00:16:09,625
I suppose a degree of
resistance is to be expected.

