00:16:12,041 --> 00:16:15,541
If memory serves,
you stole my vector machines.

241
00:16:15,625 --> 00:16:18,541
I advise all haste, madam.

242
00:16:18,625 --> 00:16:22,833
Your precious words
are poised to vanish utterly.

243
00:16:41,291 --> 00:16:43,166
Puh-Please, ma'am!
Send me up!

244
00:16:45,791 --> 00:16:47,166
Go time.

245
00:16:50,541 --> 00:16:54,375
[KOKONE]
Ah! W-Wait! That's m-my vector.

246
00:17:00,791 --> 00:17:02,125
[TSUTOMU]
Aw, crap!

247
00:17:11,125 --> 00:17:12,083
Another one!

248
00:17:12,166 --> 00:17:13,916
Kikogami?

249
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:17,708
[AKIRA] I'm sorry.
You're a threat to this world.

250
00:17:17,791 --> 00:17:19,125
He shouldn't be able to...!

251
00:17:19,208 --> 00:17:21,291
How can this
guy pilot a vector?

252
00:17:21,375 --> 00:17:23,375
[SAKURAKO] He must
have Verbalism Ability.

253
00:17:23,458 --> 00:17:25,416
Even so, how can
he man the controls

254
00:17:25,500 --> 00:17:27,708
without a suit or
the necessary training?

255
00:17:48,625 --> 00:17:50,500
[SHOKO]
No data from Vector One.

256
00:17:50,583 --> 00:17:52,375
He's gone off the grid.

257
00:17:52,458 --> 00:17:55,375
[SAKURAKO] Retrieve Kujyo's and
Domon's vectors. immediately!

258
00:17:55,458 --> 00:17:56,791
[SHOKO]
Yes, ma'am!

259
00:18:00,166 --> 00:18:02,083
[SUBETE] Yeah, I'd say
that's game, set, and match.

260
00:18:02,166 --> 00:18:05,208
[MAIA] I shall be able to
fulfill the mission very soon.

261
00:18:05,291 --> 00:18:08,833
At last my reason
for living will bear fruit.

262
00:18:08,916 --> 00:18:10,208
Your orders, ma'am?

263
00:18:10,291 --> 00:18:12,250
I'm afraid we're completely
out of working craft!

264
00:18:12,333 --> 00:18:15,791
[M.J.B.K. TWIST]
Maki!

265
00:18:15,875 --> 00:18:17,333
[FEMALE OPERATOR 1A]
The Shuto Highway and all

266
00:18:17,416 --> 00:18:19,875
major thoroughfares in the area
have been closed to traffic.

267
00:18:19,958 --> 00:18:21,666
No fatalities reported as yet.

268
00:18:21,750 --> 00:18:23,375
[FEMALE OPERATOR 1B] ...the
mysterious cloud formations

269
00:18:23,458 --> 00:18:24,791
seen over the downtown area...

270
00:18:24,875 --> 00:18:26,250
Ma'am! Look at this!

271
00:18:29,083 --> 00:18:33,208
[AKIRA] No. I won't let
it end. I made a decision.

272
00:18:33,291 --> 00:18:37,833
It's my job to protect
the world. I am The Savior.

273
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:45,750
[AKIRA]
With this hand...

274
00:18:47,666 --> 00:18:49,625
[AKIRA]
...I will save.

275
00:18:50,833 --> 00:18:52,875
Uh, do you see what I see?

276
00:18:57,291 --> 00:18:59,458
"The voice infused with
spirit bestows power

277
00:18:59,541 --> 00:19:01,708
and meaning upon our words."

278
00:19:01,791 --> 00:19:03,958
Maybe this is what the
true nature of Verbalism

279
00:19:04,041 --> 00:19:05,625
is really all about.

280
00:19:11,208 --> 00:19:12,500
Come.

281
00:19:21,583 --> 00:19:22,750
[AKIRA]
Come!

282
00:19:24,416 --> 00:19:26,541
[MAIA]
Wha... What is this?

283
00:19:31,916 --> 00:19:33,250
Maia, no!

284
00:19:37,416 --> 00:19:39,666
What's going on? The controls!

285
00:19:46,083 --> 00:19:47,541
Genesis Merge!

286
00:19:48,750 --> 00:19:50,166
[MAIA]
My voice!

287
00:19:50,250 --> 00:19:51,708
Now shout!

288
00:19:51,791 --> 00:19:54,208
--Aquarion!
--Aquarion!

289
00:20:08,708 --> 00:20:09,625
[AKIRA]
This is it.

290
00:20:09,708 --> 00:20:11,416
I've been waiting
for this moment.

291
00:20:11,500 --> 00:20:13,000
[MAIA]
What's happening to me?

292
00:20:13,083 --> 00:20:15,375
I've done this
countless time before,

293
00:20:15,458 --> 00:20:18,750
but it's never felt like this.
This is wonderful!

294
00:20:30,250 --> 00:20:31,083
--[MAIA] Kou!
--[AKIRA] Kou!

295
00:20:31,166 --> 00:20:33,875
[SUBETE]
What's going on? Maia!

296
00:20:35,666 --> 00:20:37,000
[MAIA]
I can feel it.

297
00:20:37,083 --> 00:20:40,458
You're Akira Kaibuki.

298
00:20:40,541 --> 00:20:42,000
[AKIRA]
That's right.

299
00:20:42,083 --> 00:20:44,541
And you're Maia Tsukigane.

300
00:20:51,166 --> 00:20:52,625
I know what I have to do.

301
00:20:52,708 --> 00:20:54,125
I was born for this.

302
00:20:58,791 --> 00:21:00,625
Who the hell are you?

303
00:21:01,041 --> 00:21:03,708
[M.J.B.K. TWIST]
Maki!

304
00:21:26,166 --> 00:21:28,625
[M.J.B.K. TWIST]
Maki!

305
00:21:40,291 --> 00:21:42,541
[SAKURAKO]
Incredible. Who are these two?

306
00:21:42,625 --> 00:21:45,541
[M.J.B.K. TWIST]
Maki!

307
00:21:48,166 --> 00:21:49,625
[AKIRA]
Let's go.

308
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:55,375
--[AKIRA] Mugen Punch!
--[MAIA] Mugen Punch!

309
00:22:11,083 --> 00:22:13,583
[M.J.B.K. TWIST]
Maki! Urgg!

310
00:22:18,291 --> 00:22:19,416
--[MAIA] Go!
--[AKIRA] Go!

311
00:22:50,083 --> 00:22:52,166
What the hell are
you supposed to be?

312
00:22:54,875 --> 00:22:56,916
I am The Savior.

313
00:24:27,583 --> 00:24:29,875
[KOKONE] So, thi-this
is the Preview Corner.

314
00:24:29,958 --> 00:24:31,166
[MAIA]
Hey!

315
00:24:31,250 --> 00:24:32,208
Where do you get off
appearing out of nowhere?

316
00:24:32,291 --> 00:24:33,625
That's right,
I'm talkin' to you!

317
00:24:33,708 --> 00:24:34,791
[AKIRA] When there's a
threat looming over the world.

318
00:24:34,875 --> 00:24:35,791
[MAIA]
Don't start!

319
00:24:35,875 --> 00:24:37,125
[KOKONE]
Excuse me, b-b-but, uh...

320
00:24:37,208 --> 00:24:37,958
[MAIA] I can't believe
you pulled a Merge on me!

321
00:24:38,041 --> 00:24:39,458
You dare defy Master Sougon?

322
00:24:39,541 --> 00:24:41,166
I'm The Savior. Duh.

323
00:24:41,250 --> 00:24:42,083
Will you stop saying that?

324
00:24:42,166 --> 00:24:43,208
S-Sorry, all out of time.

325
00:24:43,291 --> 00:24:44,333
N-Next episode...

326
00:24:44,416 --> 00:24:45,708
[AKIRA]
"Shine! Light of Thought."

327
00:24:45,791 --> 00:24:47,208
[MAIA]
Shut up!

